{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_49","type":"agent_message","text":"The initial “no matching coordinates” error was only the first symptom. With a temporary metadata directory in place, the Akka native test still fails at runtime from missing native-image metadata around Scala lazy-val internals. This is now squarely a missing reachability-metadata fix, so I’m using the `fix-missing-reachability-metadata` workflow to generate and validate the smallest working metadata change."}}
